title: What Is Confidence and How Do You Get It? | Samantha Peszek
description: Today's guest is Samantha Peszek. Aside from being a USA gymnast and an Olympian, she is training young girls and women to flex the muscle of confidence. In this episode, she will give us some tips as well.
